# EcoGlow â€“ Energy-Efficient Lighting Robot

## Description
**EcoGlow** is a robotics project designed to optimize home lighting using sensors. It automatically adjusts brightness based on ambient light, saving energy and promoting sustainability.

## Technologies Used
- Arduino UNO  
- Light Sensors  
- Relay Modules  
- Python  

## Key Features
- Automatic brightness adjustment  
- Energy consumption monitoring  
- Eco-friendly design  

## My Role
Designed sensor-based automation and implemented energy monitoring system.

